data.description:
NEW LOOK INSIDE!
Great 3 bedroom, 3 bath home located in the heart of Lakeview, 1 block off Harrison, with hardwood floors throughout, 2 screened in porches, a workshop and covered carport. This single story, low maintenance home has a wood burning fireplace, large and spacious living room, tons of storage and an open kitchen/dining room. The property also features a metal roof, a back deck and 2 possible primary suites.
